"content": "<p>A covering of the ground with fine particles of ice, characteristic of cold weather.</p>\n<h2>Frost is under God's control</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:16\">PSA 147:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:29\">JOB 38:29</a></p>\n<h2>Frost will be absent on the day of the LORD</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:6\">ZEC 14:6</a></p>",
